name: EncryptionMode
description:
The built-in encryption mode.
Agora recommends using AES128GCM2 or AES256GCM2 encrypted mode. These two modes support the use of salt for higher security.

parameters.AES256GCM2: 8: 256-bit AES encryption, GCM mode. This encryption mode requires the setting of salt (encryptionKdfSalt).
